    "gitCommitMessage": "Wire 'preview' channel into preview build profile\n\nMissing piece in the OTA pipeline — eas.json had no channel field, so\npreview-profile builds were produced without an expo-channel-name\nembedded. Device polled EAS Update with no channel header and EAS\nreturned nothing, even though the preview branch had updates ready.\nConfirmed root cause via eas channel:list (empty) + eas build:view\n(no channel field on eb4d78f3).\n\nAdds 'channel: preview' so future builds embed the channel and can\nresolve to the preview branch via the channel→branch mapping.\n\nThe currently-installed eb4d78f3 build still has no channel embedded\nand cannot be retrofitted — the next preview build picks this up and\nwill be the first OTA-receiving binary in practice.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
